maintext:
HARRISBURG, Pa. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Wednesday evening’s drawing of the Pennsylvania Lottery’s “Pick 5 Evening” game were:
9-3-6-2-8, Wild: 8
(nine, three, six, two, eight; Wild: eight)
